  "summary": "Parent-brand typography in Avenir: H1 Black Title Case Dark Blue/Purple; H2 Black Sentence case Dark Blue/Purple; Body/ISI body Roman Sentence case Black; ISI subheads Black ALL CAPS; Footnotes Book Sentence case Black; Campaign headline Black ALL CAPS campaign palette; Callouts black ALL CAPS per spec."
